title: Dak Prescott, Cowboys, Cam Newton, Trevor Lawrence
itunes:title: Dak Prescott, Cowboys, Cam Newton, Trevor Lawrence
description:
Colin explains why Dak Prescott should get the franchise tag, why he feels the Cowboys are not as good as they are popular, why Cam Newton's health is not the reason he isn't signed, and why he is defending Trevor Lawrence. Guests include Nick Wright, Peter King, Stephen Jackson, and Donté Stallworth.
